; Regression test for issue #811: Add options to control how CSV files are parsed (BZ#811)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/811
; The convert command uses the CSV header row to determine column mapping,
; allowing CSV files with columns in any order (e.g., amount,payee,date instead
; of the default date,posted,code,payee,amount,total,note).

test -f /dev/null convert $sourcepath/test/input/811.csv
2024/01/15 * Grocery Store
    Expenses:Unknown                             -50
    Equity:Unknown

2024/01/20 * Gas Station
    Expenses:Unknown                             -30
    Equity:Unknown
end test
